# Title: WScript or CScript Dropper - File
# Author: Tim Shelton
# Date: 2022-01-10
# Level: high
# Description: Detects a file ending in jse, vbe, js, vba, vbs written by cscript.exe or wscript.exe
# MITRE Tactic: Execution
# Tags: attack.execution, attack.t1059.005, attack.t1059.007
# Reference: https://github.com/SigmaHQ/sigma/blob/master/rules/windows/file/file_event/file_event_win_cscript_wscript_dropper.yml

Image IN ("*\\wscript.exe", "*\\cscript.exe") TargetFilename IN ("*.jse", "*.vbe", "*.js", "*.vba", "*.vbs") TargetFilename IN ("C:\\Users\\*", "C:\\ProgramData*")